  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2d rogue light action. </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exhilarating action with easy controls. Grab the relics and use your skills to conquer the tower. </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Even the toughest bosses are made easy by luck? </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687570/extras/download__6_.gif?t=1702981253\" /></span>.<br><br>I've been working on a roguelite.<br>I'd like to play some more with patterns that I've successfully built.<br>That's how I feel.<br>If you have a favorite build, you can save it and<br>You can now save your favorite builds and use them in the end content.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687570/extras/download__5_.gif?t=1702981253\" /></span>.<br><br>Dot art with movement and<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687570/extras/download__5_.gif?t=1702981253\" /></span> We focused on the moving dots and the feel of action controls.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687570/extras/download__1_.gif?t=1702981253\" /></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Since it's a roguelite game, the time per play is short</h2>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >I hope you can play it easily and enthusiastically, and forget about time. </h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2d rogue light action. </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exhilarating action with easy controls. Grab the relics and use your skills to conquer the tower. </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Even the toughest bosses are made easy by luck? </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687570/extras/download__6_.gif?t=1702981253\" /></span>.<br><br>I've been working on a roguelite.<br>I'd like to play some more with patterns that I've successfully built.<br>That's how I feel.<br>If you have a favorite build, you can save it and<br>You can now save your favorite builds and use them in the end content.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687570/extras/download__5_.gif?t=1702981253\" /></span>.<br><br>Dot art with movement and<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687570/extras/download__5_.gif?t=1702981253\" /></span> We focused on the moving dots and the feel of action controls.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687570/extras/download__1_.gif?t=1702981253\" /></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Since it's a roguelite game, the time per play is short</h2>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >I hope you can play it easily and enthusiastically, and forget about time. </h2>",
